namespace pdg { /**

\fn pdg::Serializer::serialize_1

\brief serialize 1 signed byte

Write a one byte value in the range of <b>&minus;127 to 127</b> into the data stream. 

\warning if the value is outside the range then only the info from the least significant byte will be written into the serialized data stream

\note data size: 1 byte

\sa Deserializer.deserialize_1

**/ }